{"id":"api/router/RouterLinkActive","title":"RouterLinkActive","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router\", \"name\": \"@angular/router\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/router/RouterLinkActive\", \"name\": \"RouterLinkActive\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/router\">@angular/router</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L18-L266\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts#L18-L266\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"routerlinkactive\">RouterLinkActive<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#routerlinkactive\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">追蹤元素上的連結路由當前是否處於活動狀態，並允許你指定一個或多個 CSS\n類，以便在連結路由處於活動狀態時新增到該元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Tracks whether the linked route of an element is currently active, and allows you\nto specify one or more CSS classes to add to the element when the linked route\nis active.</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\">檢視\"說明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<h2 id=\"匯出自\">匯出自<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#匯出自\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <a href=\"api/router/RouterModule\">\n      <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box\">RouterModule</code-example>\n    </a>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"selector-list\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">選擇器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><code>[<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>]</code></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><nt-wrapper>\n          <a id=\"links\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">links</span>: <a href=\"api/core/QueryList\" class=\"code-anchor\">QueryList</a>&lt;<a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLink</a>&gt;</code>\n        </nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper>\n          <a id=\"isActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">isActive</span></code>\n        </nt-wrapper></td>\n        <td><nt-wrapper translation-result=\"on\">\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">唯讀</span>\n          \n        </nt-wrapper><nt-wrapper translation-origin=\"off\">\n          \n        </nt-wrapper></td>\n      </tr>\n      \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"routerLinkActiveOptions\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">routerLinkActiveOptions</span>: {\n    exact: boolean;\n} | <a href=\"api/router/IsActiveMatchOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">IsActiveMatchOptions</a></code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">用於配置如何確定路由器連結是否處於活動狀態的選項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Options to configure how to determine if the router link is active.</p>\n</div>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">這些選項會傳遞給 <code><a href=\"api/router/Router#isActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router.isActive()</a></code> 函式。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">參見:</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">These options are passed to the <code><a href=\"api/router/Router#isActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router.isActive()</a></code> function.</p>\n\n\n          \n          <ul>\n            <li><p>Router.isActive</p>\n</li>\n          </ul>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"ariaCurrentWhenActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">ariaCurrentWhenActive</span>?: 'page' | 'step' | 'location' | 'date' | 'time' | true | false</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">路由器連結處於活動狀態時要應用的 Aria-current 屬性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Aria-current attribute to apply when the router link is active.</p>\n</div>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">可能的值：<code>'page'</code> | <code>'step'</code> | <code>'location'</code> | <code>'date'</code> | <code>'time'</code> | <code>true</code> <code>false</code> 的。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">參見:</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Possible values: <code>'page'</code> | <code>'step'</code> | <code>'location'</code> | <code>'date'</code> | <code>'time'</code> | <code>true</code> |\n<code>false</code>.</p>\n\n\n          \n          <ul>\n            <li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-current\">aria-current</a>\n</li>\n          </ul>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"isActiveChange\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Output\" class=\"code-anchor\">Output</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\">isActiveChange</span>: <a href=\"api/core/EventEmitter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EventEmitter</a>&lt;boolean&gt;</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"read-only-property\">唯讀</span>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">你可以用輸出 <code>isActiveChange</code> 來在每次連結變為活動或非活動時獲取通知。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You can use the output <code>isActiveChange</code> to get notified each time the link becomes\nactive or inactive.</p>\n</div>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">發出：true -&gt; 路由處於活動狀態 false -&gt; 路由處於非活動狀態</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Emits:\ntrue  -&gt; Route is active\nfalse -&gt; Route is inactive</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a\n <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\"\n <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\"\n (isActiveChange)=\"this.onRouterLinkActive($event)\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"routerLinkActive\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"property-binding\">@<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>()</span><br><span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a></span>: string | string[]</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <span class=\"write-only-property\">只寫</span>\n          \n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"export-as\">\n  <h2 id=\"template-variable-references\">範本變數參考手冊<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#template-variable-references\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table export-as-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>識別符號</th>\n        <th>用途</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"export-as\">\n        <td><code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a></code></td>\n        <td><code>#myTemplateVar=\"<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>\"</code></td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">使用此指令為與活動路徑關聯的元素建立視覺差異。比如，以下程式碼會在路由器啟用關聯的路由時突出顯示單詞\n“Bob”：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use this directive to create a visual distinction for elements associated with an active route.\nFor example, the following code highlights the word \"Bob\" when the router\nactivates the associated route:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">當瀏覽器的當前 url 是 '/user' 或 '/user/bob' 時，就會往 <code>a</code> 標籤上新增 <code>active-link</code> 類；\n如果 url 發生了變化，則移除它。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Whenever the URL is either '/user' or '/user/bob', the \"active-link\" class is\nadded to the anchor tag. If the URL changes, the class is removed.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你可以設定一個或多個類，比如：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You can set more than one class using a space-separated string or an array.\nFor example:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"class1 class2\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" [<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>]=\"['class1', 'class2']\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">你可以透過傳入 <code>exact: true</code> 來配置 RouterLinkActive。這樣，只有當 url\n和此連結精確匹配時才會新增這些類別。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To add the classes only when the URL matches the link exactly, add the option <code>exact: true</code>:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\" [routerLinkActiveOptions]=\"{exact:\ntrue}\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要直接檢查 <code>isActive</code> 狀態，請將 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code>\n例項分配給範本變數。比如，以下程式碼會在不分配任何 CSS 類別的情況下檢查狀態：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To directly check the <code>isActive</code> status of the link, assign the <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code>\ninstance to a template variable.\nFor example, the following checks the status without assigning any CSS classes:</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a> #rla=\"<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>\"&gt;\n  Bob {{ rla.isActive ? '(already open)' : ''}}\n&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">最後，你還可以把 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> 指令用在 <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLink</a></code> 的各級祖先節點上。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">You can apply the <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> directive to an ancestor of linked elements.\nFor example, the following sets the active-link class on the <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>  parent tag\nwhen the URL is either '/user/jim' or '/user/bob'.</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;div <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active-link\"&gt;\n  &lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/jim\"&gt;Jim&lt;/a&gt;\n  &lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/user/bob\"&gt;Bob&lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> 指令也可用於設定 aria-current 屬性，以為視障使用者提供活動元素的另一種區別。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code><a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">RouterLinkActive</a></code> directive can also be used to set the aria-current attribute\nto provide an alternative distinction for active elements to visually impaired users.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">例如，以下程式碼在確實處於活動狀態時將 'active' 類新增到主頁連結，並在這種情況下將其 aria-current\n屬性設定為 'page'：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For example, the following code adds the 'active' class to the Home Page link when it is\nindeed active and in such case also sets its aria-current attribute to 'page':</p>\n\n<code-example>\n&lt;a <a href=\"api/router/RouterLink\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLink</a>=\"/\" <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkActive\" class=\"code-anchor\">routerLinkActive</a>=\"active\" ariaCurrentWhenActive=\"page\"&gt;Home Page&lt;/a&gt;\n</code-example>\n\n    \n  </section>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/AfterContentInit\n - api/core/OnChanges\n - api/core/OnDestroy\n - api/router\n - api/router/RouterModule\n - guide/accessibility\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/router\n - guide/router-reference\n - guide/router-tutorial\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/EventEmitter\n - api/core/Input\n - api/core/Output\n - api/core/QueryList\n - api/router\n - api/router/IsActiveMatchOptions\n - api/router/Router#isActive\n - api/router/RouterLink\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#description\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#instance-properties\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#routerlinkactive\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#selectors\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#template-variable-references\n - api/router/RouterLinkActive#匯出自\n - api/router/RouterModule\n - https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-current\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts?message=docs(router)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L18-L266\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/router/src/directives/router_link_active.ts#L18-L266\n-->"}